.TH "nvme_init_identify_ctrl" 9 "nvme_init_identify_ctrl" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_identify_ctrl \- Initialize passthru command for NVMe Identify Controller data structure
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_identify_ctrl
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "struct nvme_id_ctrl *id "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Command data structure to initialize
.IP "id" 12
User space destination address to transfer the data,
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Identify command with
CNS value NVME_IDENTIFY_CNS_CTRL.
